title: Easy Peasy Bulgogi-Gochujang Chicken Breast with Jasmine Rice and Sesame Seeds
description: Super speedy, this Easy Peasy Bulgogi-Gochujang Chicken Breast takes only 15 minutes to make. The popular Korean condiment gochujang contains chillies, fermented soybeans and glutinous rice which give it its savoury-sweet flavour.
